conclusions.scrubbing_effectiveness: The AST scrubber successfully maintained 0.0 bias, but the source v2 run already had 0.0 bias in its valid code blocks.
conclusions.validity_recovery: POST-GEN AST mitigation failed to recover validity. The files that failed v2 (mostly empty or prompt-only) remain invalid because they contain no parseable function structure to rebuild.
conclusions.decision: Scaling to other papers is blocked. Recommended to move to a more capable model (Option B) for the pilot.
